    <string name="asset_setup_title">Game assets required</string>
    <string name="asset_setup_description">This app needs original game files from Heroes of Might and Magic III: Shadow of Death (or Complete Edition). These files cannot be bundled with the app due to copyright.\n\nCopy the file H3sprite.lod from the Data folder of your game installation to your phone, then select it below.\n\nNote: HD Edition, Restoration of Erathia, and Armageddon\'s Blade are not supported.</string>
    <string name="asset_setup_select_button">Select H3sprite.lod</string>

    <string name="asset_setup_hota_title">HotA assets (optional)</string>
    <string name="asset_setup_hota_description">If you have Horn of the Abyss, you can add its sprites. Download the official HotA installer (HotA_*_setup.exe) from hota.acidcave.net and select it below — the app will extract the required data automatically.\n\nHotA 1.7.x and 1.8.0 (Bulwark) are supported.</string>
    <string name="asset_setup_hota_select_button">Select HotA installer</string>

